# oMLX model manifest (rendered by chezmoi).
#
# Format (pipe-delimited, one model per line):
#   <hf-repo-id>|<local-dir-name>
#
# - hf-repo-id: Hugging Face repo id (e.g. "mlx-community/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-4bit")
# - local-dir-name: subdirectory under ~/.omlx/models/ where weights land
#
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored.
#
# Downloads are opt-in via the `downloadOmlxModels` data variable in
# ~/.config/chezmoi/chezmoi.toml. Re-prompt by clearing that value.
#
# Strategy: Heretic/Abliterated lineage only. Refusal-removed models that
# preserve base-model intelligence (KL divergence ~0.0107 nats on the Qwen
# checkpoint — ~15x cleaner than community abliteration references). Stock
# mlx-community variants were dropped because the KL delta to the heretic
# counterparts is negligible on agentic-coding workloads and we use one
# model at a time in an agent. Qwen ships in two precision tiers: 4-bit is
# universal; the 6-bit quality tier is gated to the personal profile
# (isWork=false) because 27.2 GB weights + long-ctx KV cache blows past the
# 25 GB default weights budget on 36 GB work hosts.

# Gemma-4 26B-A4B heretic (MoE, ~4B active / 26B total, 256k ctx, ~14.5 GB).
# Only 4-bit is published by mlx-community. Serves as the fast small-active
# model for low-latency agent turns.
# https://huggingface.co/mlx-community/gemma-4-26B-A4B-it-heretic-4bit
mlx-community/gemma-4-26B-A4B-it-heretic-4bit|gemma-4-26b-a4b-it-heretic-4bit

# Qwen3.6 35B-A3B Abliterated+Heretic @ 4-bit (~22 GB) — speed tier.
# Default on the 36 GB M3 Pro where the 6-bit would saturate memory at long ctx.
# https://huggingface.co/Youssofal/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-Abliterated-Heretic-MLX-4bit
Youssofal/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-Abliterated-Heretic-MLX-4bit|qwen3.6-abliterated-heretic-4bit

{{ if ne .isWork true -}}
# Qwen3.6 35B-A3B Abliterated+Heretic @ 6-bit (~27.2 GB) — quality tier.
# Same abliteration checkpoint as the 4-bit above, higher precision. Gated
# to personal-profile hosts (isWork=false): the 64 GB M1 Pro fits 27 GB
# weights + long-ctx KV cache + server overhead under a ~50 GB model budget;
# the 36 GB M3 Pro would exceed the 25 GB default weights budget even before
# KV, so this entry renders empty there.
# https://huggingface.co/Youssofal/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-Abliterated-Heretic-MLX-6bit
Youssofal/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-Abliterated-Heretic-MLX-6bit|qwen3.6-abliterated-heretic-6bit
{{- end }}
